hcc_text: Morningstar Road is a pedestrian high crash corridor (top third for pedestrian deaths and serious injuries per mile in Staten Island)
info: At Morningstar Road at Hooker Place, Dr M L King Exwy Sb Exit 13 and Dr Mlk Exwy Nb En Morningstar Road, there were 7 injuries in crashes between 2008 and 2012.
